    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: this submission conforms to the Minimal profile and does not include a structured Context of Use object; the intended use scope is described narratively in the package description.",
